#META# contentSummary: Acknowledgment (*iqrār*) deed concerning a lease of three parcels of land owned by Abū Naṣr b. Dāniyāl in the village of Rām K.rī/K.ray. *Verso* contains a note written in Judeo-Persian, summarizing the details of the acknowledgment. The three parcels of land are mentioned in one of Abū Naṣr b. Dāniyāl 's ledgers (see the comment below on l. 5).
